Description: From the P2P mission in Mozambique, it was recommended on a common narrative grounded on human rights and humanitarian principles based on a joint data analysis. Mozambique humanitarian community has a 2024 HNRP that targets 1.7M people out of the 2.5M in need. The HCT and ICCG endorsed a monitoring plan that will guide us on the analysis based on the monthly 5W data from clusters and other baseline data eg DTM data on IDPs, returnees, and newly displaced (ETT).

Description: Develop a Power BI dashboard to monitor support requests logged via the Jira service desk. This dashboard will be shared with BHA and MSI (for TPM), as well as the iMMAP Africa Desk to provide transparent and up-to-date insight into the types of requests received and partners' satisfaction with the requests. The dashboard will also serve to maintain the Indicator Tracking Table and output summary used in the monthly/semi-annual/annual/final reports provided to BHA.
